Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 23:14:12 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 04/40] Add config.mk DSL parser with 84 unit tests
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Python parser for the config.mk design DSL that extracts structural
params (PLATFORM, DESIGN_NAME, VERILOG_FILES, SDC_FILE, BLOCKS) and
flow arguments (CORE_UTILIZATION, PLACE_DENSITY, etc.) for generating
orfs_flow() Bazel targets.

Handles all DSL features: export/=/?=/:=, line continuations,
$(wildcard), $(sort), variable resolution. Emits deprecation warnings
for complex features (ifeq, $(if), $(filter)).

84 unit tests including integration tests against all real config.mk
files in the repository.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Signed-off-by: Øyvind Harboe <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
